<bibRefCitation author="Bezark, L. G." box="[1098,1254,725,751]" pageId="2" pageNumber="581" refId="ref4783" refString="Bezark, L. G. (2021 a) A photographic Catalog of the Cerambycidae of the World. New World Cerambycidae Catalog. Available from: http: // bezbycids. com / byciddb / wdefault. asp? w = n (accessed 12 August 2021)" type="url" year="2021">Bezark 2021a</bibRefCitation>
